	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/06/18/morning-agenda-suntrust-in-mortgage-settlement/" data-title="Morning Agenda: SunTrust in Mortgage Settlement" data-description="The Justice Department reaches a settlement with SunTrust over mortgage practices. | An S.E.C. filing from William A. Ackman concerning his Allergan bid contains an error. | A mortgage deal is under scrutiny. | Argentina is moving to circumvent a Supreme Court order on the country&#039;s debt.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
